      <title>作为马斯克的Doge Push的一部分，财政部计划“实质性”裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/treasury-plans-substantial-layoffs-as-part-of-musk-s-doge-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据该部门官员在法院案件中提交的语言，美国财政部正计划通过减少埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）领导的美国政府规模来裁定“大量雇员”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/treasury-plans-substantial-layoffs-as-part-of-musk-s-doge-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:16:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯在旅途中访问格陵兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/vance-to-visit-greenland-on-trip-that-s-inflamed-local-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统杰德·万斯（JD Vance）表示，他将在本周访问格陵兰的代表团中，尽管这次旅行引发了丹麦领土上当地领导人的批评，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示应该受到美国的控制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/vance-to-visit-greenland-on-trip-that-s-inflamed-local-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚的卫生系统涉足药物短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/colombia-s-health-system-teeters-with-medication-in-short-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[政府独立的人权监督机构警告说，哥伦比亚卫生系统的危机未能为患者提供医疗服务和药物的机会而达到“关键”水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/colombia-s-health-system-teeters-with-medication-in-short-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:02:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普停止了一些绿卡申请，以提高审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-halts-some-green-card-applications-in-bid-to-boost-vetting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府暂停了一些绿卡申请，因为它试图对潜在的永久居民进行审查，这是对美国移民系统进行深远大修的最新一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-halts-some-green-card-applications-in-bid-to-boost-vetting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他会“爱”为广播公司NPR，PBS退还</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-says-he-would-love-to-defund-broadcasters-npr-pbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，他赞成向国家公共广播电台和公共广播服务提供资金，对他不利，并浪费了纳税人的钱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-says-he-would-love-to-defund-broadcasters-npr-pbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 19:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署行政命令加强选民注册标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-signs-executive-order-to-toughen-voter-registration-standards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周二签署了一项行政命令，该命令将寻求向不采用更严格的选民注册标准的各州削减联邦赠款，这是共和党在获得选民劳斯莱斯的政治斗争中的最新一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-signs-executive-order-to-toughen-voter-registration-standards</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 19:38:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普指示财政部现代化支付系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-directs-treasury-department-to-centralize-digitize-payment-systems</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）指示财政部对其付款系统进行现代化和集中化，以扎根欺诈行为，因为金钱在整个联邦政府中转移。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-directs-treasury-department-to-centralize-digitize-payment-systems</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 19:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信号应用程序受Houthi Chat Uproar中心的激进主义者评价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/signal-app-favored-by-activists-at-center-of-houthi-strike-chat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府官员用来讨论对也门的胡塞叛军的攻击的消息传递信号是由一次无政府主义者创建的，以帮助激进主义者，记者和其他人在政府情报机构的窥视之外进行交流，并交流。不计划政府军事行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/signal-app-favored-by-activists-at-center-of-houthi-strike-chat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 17:44:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普审查信号应用程序的使用，在聊天泄漏后为华尔兹辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他的政府正在调查一名新闻记者向也门的一组高级官员，讨论军事罢工计划，但表示支持国家安全顾问迈克尔·沃尔兹（Michael Waltz）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-backs-waltz-after-breach-on-houthi-strike-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 13:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国说，即使俄罗斯列出条款，黑海休战也同意了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国表示，俄罗斯和乌克兰同意在黑海停火，尽管克里姆林宫表示，其参与将取决于一系列先决条件，包括制裁救济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/us-says-russia-ukraine-agree-ceasefire-in-black-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:07:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
